THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS

This project includes the QRCode library by Richard Moore (ricmoo),
licensed under the MIT License:
https://github.com/ricmoo/QRCode

Map data (src/EuMapData.h) is derived from:

- Natural Earth (https://www.naturalearthdata.com/) - country borders, 1:10m.
  Public domain. Obtained via the world-atlas TopoJSON redistribution
  (https://github.com/topojson/world-atlas), which is ISC licensed.

- GeoNames (https://www.geonames.org/) - city locations and population.
  Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0):
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
  ATTRIBUTION REQUIRED: if you redistribute this project or a derivative,
  you must credit GeoNames. The notice above satisfies this.

Data sources used by this software have their own terms:
- adsb.fi (https://adsb.fi/) - personal, non-commercial use only
- ip-api.com (https://ip-api.com/)

Please review their terms before commercial deployment. In particular,
adsb.fi's free API is intended for personal use — commercial products
should arrange appropriate data access.
